channel.title: Plant Project...ugh
channel.description:
Okay this is my first time posting on the homework section for help, I usually don't have problems with homework.... But, I need help now so I'd really appreciate it if you could, thank you.
Ok, I have to do this plant porject. Gotta find 15 plants and their seeds, and press the plants. Don't worry about that part, I'm just giving you an overview. I also need to find the scientific names of plants, fruits, vegetables, trees, etc. That's where I'm having lots of toruble, I can't seem to find a good site that gives me the names.
Could someone help me find a site that tells you what the scientific names of plants, tree, vegetalbes, etc., like some sort of index? You can post multiple sites if one doesn't have them all, or you can just help me partially by just posting one or w/e. If you can find a solution that doesn't require the internet feel free to post it.
I sincerely thank whoever helps me out on this.
